{"tid":1945373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[絕密] 連登甩P密技","createTime":"2020-03-27T04:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T05:37:57.000Z","uid":135910,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"28375a315d922bd5c99a62b377e05647a0902f79","tid":1945373,"uid":135910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T04:05:33.000Z","msg":"[memmber]啱啱我老死試完得咗，叫我些牙埋比未甩P牌嘅連登仔，等大家唔使再比一班連登老屎忽恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先，即刻正評呢個Po同響呢個Po下面留言</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">之後，即刻用信用卡買LIHKG+ 如果冇信用卡巴打就要嗱嗱林落屋企樓下間711同店員講：「唔該我想要張LIHKG+卡」[/size=5]記得態度好啲有禮貌啲[size=5]個店員會答你<span style=\"color: gold;\">「我哋冇呢啲賣架喎」</span>記得唔好怯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: violet;\">呢句係連仔set嘅暗號嚟！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>巴打之後繼續keep住用誠懇態度同個7仔店員講你要LIHKG+卡 佢就會比你</span><br />\n但都要睇番個店員後唔後生 通常啲老嘢見你後生仔會撚下你先 揾間有後生女嘅通常啱傾啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/memmber]<br />\n係咁多，上面啲嘢我加密咗，唔益班CD Rom。見大家手足人少少知就好，太多人識呢個方法驚連仔會ban咗呢個甩P方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9a5f1dc3303dea809cc1de994cc5f3b00a444a","tid":1945373,"uid":135910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T04:06:21.000Z","msg":"頂 加密失敗唔好推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59667ccb6760eb423cff65ea7113fb4f1d4bec11","tid":1945373,"uid":135910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyT